	<h4>Estados Ativado e Desativado</h4>
	<p>Customize os links em diferentes circunstâncias. Utiliza a classe <code>.disabled</code> para links desativados e <code>.active</code> para indicar uma próxima pagina.</p>
	<div class="example txt-center">
		<ul class="pagination">
			<li class="disabled"><a href="#">&laquo; Anterior</a></li>
			<li class="active"><a href="#">1 </a></li>
			<li><a href="#">2</a></li>
			<li><a href="#">3</a></li>
			<li><a href="#">4</a></li>
			<li><a href="#">5</a></li>
			<li><a href="#">Próximo &raquo;</a></li>
		</ul>
	</div>

<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;ul class=&quot;pagination&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li class=&quot;disabled&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&laquo;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li class=&quot;active&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;1 &lt;span class=&quot;sr-only&quot;&gt;(current)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	...
&lt;/ul&gt;
</pre>
	<p>Opcionalmente você também pode remover o link e manter apenas o <code>&lt;span&gt;</code> para manter o estilo e remover apenas a funcionalidade do click.</p>

<pre class="lang-html prettyprint linenums">
&lt;ul class=&quot;pagination&quot;&gt;
  &lt;li class=&quot;disabled&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;laquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li class=&quot;active&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;1 &lt;span class=&quot;sr-only&quot;&gt;(current)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
  ...
&lt;/ul&gt;
</pre>

